      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and release notes demonstrating QA procedures consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 was used under a validated QA framework including regression test suite and controlled release. Version control logs and test reports reviewed. Achieved level meets required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
