      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensional analysis must confirm that non-dimensional groups (Reynolds number, flow coefficient, head coefficient) match between validation experiments and COU operating conditions within 5%.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds number, flow coefficient, and head coefficient computed for all five operating points. Maximum deviation between validation experiment and COU non-dimensional parameters is 3.1%. Equivalency of input parameters confirmed."
