    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification confirms P90 hemolysis prediction remains below clinical threshold with 18% margin. Independent review completed. Hemolysis model calibration methodology is consistent with established correlation approaches in the rotary blood pump literature. Assessment team accepts the computational evidence as sufficient to support the regulatory submission at MRL 5 for Class III VAD device.",
